android.car

类 SyncResultCallback<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.SyncResultCallback<V>
  • 类型参数:
    V - refer to a Parcelable object.
    所有已实现的接口:
    ResultCallback<V>

    public final class SyncResultCallback<V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ResultCallback<V>
    Synchronous implementation for ResultCallback.

    Can be used to get the results synchronously where ResultCallback is required. get() and get(long, TimeUnit) methods can be used to get the result.

      • get

        public V get(long timeout,
             java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit unit)
      throws java.lang.InterruptedException,
             java.util.concurrent.TimeoutException
        Waits if necessary for at most the given time for the computation to complete, and then retrieves its result, if available.
        参数:
        timeout - the maximum time to wait
        unit - the time unit of the timeout argument
        返回:
        the computed result
        抛出:
        java.lang.InterruptedException - if the current thread was interrupted while waiting
        java.util.concurrent.TimeoutException - if the wait timed out
